1. Volim da pijem *alkohol* sa prijateljima. (I like to drink *alcohol* with friends.)
2. On je stalno govorio o štetnosti *alkohola*. (He constantly talked about the harmfulness of *alcohol*.)
3. Koliko *alkohola* ima u ovom piću? (How much *alcohol* is in this drink?)
4. Dugo sam se borio sa zavisnošću od *alkohola*. (I struggled with alcohol addiction for a long time.)
5. Naša vlada povećava porez na prodaju *alkohola*. (Our government is increasing taxes on the sale of *alcohol*.)
6. Nije dobro da voziš posle konzumiranja *alkohola*. (It's not good to drive after consuming *alcohol*.)
7. Ova kafa ima ukus *alkohola*. (This coffee has a taste of *alcohol*.)
8. Konzumiranje *alkohola* u prevelikim količinama može biti opasno po zdravlje. (Consuming *alcohol* in excessive amounts can be dangerous for health.)
9. Njegovo ponašanje se menja kada popije *alkohol*. (His behavior changes when he drinks *alcohol*.)
10. Moramo smanjiti potrošnju *alkohola* da bismo poboljšali svoje zdravlje. (We need to reduce our consumption of *alcohol* to improve our health.)